(1 - y)^p \approx 1 - py
y
x_0 \approx \frac{1}{2p+1}
 2(p+1)x^p - px - 2 = 0 
x = 1 - \frac{r}{p}
x^p \approx e^{-r}
2(p+1) e^{-r} + r = p+2.
p
r \approx 1
r \approx \ln 2
r = \ln 2 + s
(p+1) e^{-s} + \ln 2 + s = (p+2).
s
p
(p+1)(1 - s) + \ln 2 + s = (p+2)
s = \frac{\ln 2 - 1}{p}
x \approx 1 - \frac{\ln 2}{p} + \frac{1 - \ln 2}{p^2}.
